summary: Transforms Jarl Ulfric Stormcloak... into a WOMAN!
descriptionHtml:
The only thing Jarl Ulfric Stormcloak ever wanted was for Skryim\'s ultimate freedom from the tyrranical Legionaires. 

But secretly, he always had another wish... 

TO BECOME A WOMAN! And a sexy one at that! Now, his dream came true with the help of a mysterious persona\'s magical potion. 

The only drawback of such, is that he still has his sexy man-drawl, but he loves his voice too much to change it. 

*This is purely a joke! I made this because it was the easiest mod to make, ever*
author: Kasaru
